Steps To Reproduce:
1) remove (or temporarily rename) your report_options.xml;
2) start gramps, then say Reports => Books => Book Report;
3) create a new book, with two (text) Descendant Reports;
4) configure the first report using the Style Editor to
   create a style with the title font being 14-point;
5) configure the second report using the Style Editor to
   create a style with the title font being 48-point;
6) view the result (I use PDF but I believe it does not
   matter) and observe both report's titles are 48-point.
